# Cloudflare Workers static-assets response headers.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/headers/
# Astro copies public/ verbatim into dist/, where Workers parses this file
# (it is not itself served as an asset).
#
# Conservative, theme-safe hardening only. A full enforcing Content-Security-
# Policy (script-src/style-src/font-src) is intentionally omitted — it needs
# testing against Starlight's inline styles, Google Fonts, and Pagefind first.
# HSTS is managed at the Cloudflare zone level (SSL/TLS → Edge Certificates),
# not here, so Cloudflare can handle the preload commitment safely.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'none'
